s:21:\"tempera_slideSpecific\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"tempera_slideCateg\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"tempera_slideNumber\";i:5;s:18:\"tempera_sliderimg1\";s:90:\"http://localhost/agriculture_fr/wp-content/themes/tempera/images/slider/tempera-slide1.jpg\";s:20:\"tempera_slidertitle1\";s:14:\"Jump right in!\";s:19:\"tempera_slidertext1\";s:280:\"It\'s like plunging into the calm ocean, the wind softly caressing your tanned body, the sun warming and igniting it. It\'s like feeling the ocean cool and\r\n						embrace and contain you like a primordial womb. It\'s also like waking up from this dream and getting back to your blog!\";s:19:\"tempera_sliderlink1\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"tempera_sliderimg2\";s:90:\"http://localhost/agriculture_fr/wp-content/themes/tempera/images/slider/tempera-slide2.jpg\";s:20:\"tempera_slidertitle2\";s:34:\"Tempera brings the mountain to you\";s:19:\"tempera_slidertext2\";s:203:\"Remember that mountain you\'ve always wanted to climb? Tempera will not only get it to come to you but it will also provide hiking equipment and if needed \r\n						will actually climb the mountain for you.\";s:19:\"tempera_sliderlink2\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"tempera_sliderimg3\";s:90:\"http://localhost/agriculture_fr/wp-content/themes/tempera/images/slider/tempera-slide3.jpg\";s:20:\"tempera_slidertitle3\";s:35:\"Using Tempera is a walk in the park\";s:19:\"tempera_slidertext3\";s:278:\"Using Tempera is really just a walk in the park. If in that park you\'ll meet a baby, using Tempera will become as easy as taking candy from that baby.\r\n						If there\'s a picnic going on and there\'s cake, you can consider yourself invited and things will become a piece of cake.\";s:19:\"tempera_sliderlink3\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"tempera_sliderimg4\";s:90:\"http://localhost/agriculture_fr/wp-content/themes/tempera/images/slider/tempera-slide4.jpg\";s:20:\"tempera_slidertitle4\";s:37:\"Tempera lives up to your expectations\";s:19:\"tempera_slidertext4\";s:233:\"Especially if your expectations are fluffy clouds. In that case it may even surpass your expectations; then your expectations will start having \r\n						expectations of their own which of course Tempera will be able to fulfil as well.\";s:19:\"tempera_sliderlink4\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"tempera_sliderimg5\";s:90:\"http://localhost/agriculture_fr/wp-content/themes/tempera/images/slider/tempera-slide5.jpg\";s:20:\"tempera_slidertitle5\";s:32:\"Tempera is a breath of fresh air\";s:19:\"tempera_slidertext5\";s:237:\"It\'s like being on a frozen mountain top. It\'s like getting there and not being able to climb back down. It\'s like having to survive in that hostile\r\n						environment for months just by eating insects and drinking tea made out of twigs.\";s:19:\"tempera_sliderlink5\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"tempera_columnType\";s:14:\"Widget Columns\";s:22:\"tempera_columnSpecific\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"tempera_columnCateg\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"tempera_columnNumber\";i:3;s:17:\"tempera_nrcolumns\";i:3;s:22:\"tempera_colimageheight\";i:201;s:21:\"tempera_colimagewidth\";s:3:\"318\";s:22:\"tempera_columnreadmore\";s:9:\"Read more\";s:18:\"tempera_fronttext1\";s:74:\"Tempera is living on the edge, waiting for you to come and give it a push!\";s:18:\"tempera_fronttext3\";s:628:\"Above and below the columns you have editable titles and text fields. The text fields suppport <em>HTML</em> tags and [shortcodes] so you can turn the \r\n							Presentation Page into your personal playground. You can add, remove and edit all this and much more from the Tempera Settings page.<br>\r\n							While you can show your latest posts on the Presentation Page, you can also use the <u>Blog</u> page template to designate another page as your primary\r\n							blog posts page.<br><br>\r\n							<div style=\'text-align:center\'><strong>As you can see, with Tempera the sky\'s the limit. Just remember to have fun!</strong></div>\";s:18:\"tempera_fronttext2\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"tempera_fronttext4\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"tempera_fontsize\";s:4:\"15px\";s:18:\"tempera_fontfamily\"